snippet.title: TOBOR STEAM Official Release on 16th of November
snippet.description:
TOBOR official release: 16th of Nov. 2023

Wishlist TOBOR on Steam Now!

🚨 SHARE SOME LOVE IN THE COMMENTS!! Let us know if you enjoyed this episode! It helps us determine if we should keep working on this series and sharing our design & coding processes!

TOBOR is a spy simulation game where your mission is to observe an insane world using a surveillance camera. You have 7 days to gather intelligence and investigate the tragic story of Undercroft.
►https://store.steampowered.com/app/2081310/TOBOR/

In Tobor : Your Mission is 
👀To observe an insane world on a surveillance
🎮Gather Intel on the subjects
🔍Find out the truth
